  "remarks": "A suspected military employee of the Main Intelligence Directorate of the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation (GRU); leader of the so-called ‘Donetsk People’s Republic’.  Stepped down from role in Donetsk in August 2014.  Returned to Russia and is believed to be in several left-wing \"patriotic\" organisations including Head of ‘Novorossia’ public movement.  Former ‘Minister of Defence’ of the so-called ‘Donetsk People's Republic’. Remains active in supporting separatist activity in eastern Ukraine.  One of the organisers of the ‘Russian March’ in November 2016; Listing: Listed on 19 Jun. 2014 (re-listed on 16 Jun. 2017, 10 June 2020 and 10 June 2023)",
